OL,3,CTenants feel 'hopeless' and 'trapped
OL,4,Cby broken housing system'
OL,6,FITV News' Max Walsh spoke to people
OL,7,Fabout their experience of the rental
OL,8,Fmarket.
OL,10,FRenters in Bristol say they feel
OL,11,F'trapped' and 'hopeless' as the number
OL,12,Fof evictions rise and city's
OL,13,Fspiralling rents are forcing more
OL,14,Fpeople out of the city.
OL,16,FBristol has become the most expensive
OL,17,Fplace to rent outside of London.
