OL,3,CTenants feel 'hopeless' and 'trapped
OL,4,Cby broken housing system'
OL,6,FAhead of the July's General Election,
OL,7,Fvoters in the city are urging the next
OL,8,Fgovernment to prioritise housing to
OL,9,Fhelp lower costs and improve tenants'
OL,10,Frights.
OL,12,FStacey Nickel has been living in her
OL,13,Frented accommodation with her son for
OL,14,Ffive years but she's been issued with
OL,15,Fa no-fault eviction from her landlord
OL,16,Fand faces having to move out in
OL,17,FSeptember.
