OL,3,CTenants feel 'hopeless' and 'trapped
OL,4,Cby broken housing system'
OL,6,FShe says the enormous increase in
OL,7,Frents, that has seen the city's
OL,8,Faverage rent rise to #1,756, means she
OL,9,Fcan no longer afford to the live in
OL,10,Fthe area where she runs a business and
OL,11,Fher son goes to school.
OL,13,FStacey said: "No matter what I do, all
OL,14,FI can think about is the fact that
OL,15,FI've got to move and that I cannot
OL,16,Ffind anywhere to live.
