OL,3,CTenants feel 'hopeless' and 'trapped
OL,4,Cby broken housing system'
OL,6,F"It just feels impossible. Knowing
OL,7,Fthat the council cannot help me either
OL,8,Fbecause there are no council
OL,9,Fproperties. Sometimes I just feel
OL,10,Fquite hopeless."
OL,12,FStacey wants to see the next
OL,13,Fgovernment prioritise building more
OL,14,Faffordable properties and to increase
OL,15,Fthe number of council homes to take
OL,16,Fthe pressure off the private rental
OL,17,Fmarket.
OL,19,FThere are currently more than 20,000
OL,20,Fpeople on the council housing waiting
OL,21,Flist in Bristol.
