OL,3,CTenants feel 'hopeless' and 'trapped
OL,4,Cby broken housing system'
OL,6,FOn the Downs, everywhere you look,
OL,7,Fthere are caravans parked up. In the
OL,8,Flast four years the numbers of people
OL,9,Fchoosing to live in vehicles has sky-
OL,10,Frocketed.
OL,12,FIt's estimated there are now up 650
OL,13,Fvan-dwellers in the city, a number
OL,14,Fwhich has quadrupled since 2020.
OL,16,FNathaneal Hunt-Crabtree, who works for
OL,17,Fthe ambulance service, moved into his
OL,18,Fvan with his girlfriend after being
OL,19,Fevicted from his rented accommodation.
OL,20,FHe says it is currently the only
OL,21,Fviable option.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
