OL,3,CTenants feel 'hopeless' and 'trapped
OL,4,Cby broken housing system'
OL,6,FHe said: "We've been priced out of
OL,7,FBristol for the last four years but
OL,8,Fwe've just been trying to cling on a
OL,9,Fbit to see if we can still make it -
OL,10,Fbut it's just not worth it.
OL,12,F"The sort of properties me and my
OL,13,Fgirlfriend can afford is not just
OL,14,Ffeasible. This van is bigger than the
OL,15,Fproperties I would get. Trying to get
OL,16,Fa property in this city is
OL,17,Fridiculously hard."
OL,19,FNathaneal wants to see more done to
OL,20,Fprotect tenants' rights.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
