OL,3,CTenants feel 'hopeless' and 'trapped
OL,4,Cby broken housing system'
OL,6,FAlly Rush, from charity Shelter in
OL,7,FBristol, said Bristol's whole rental
OL,8,Fmarket was 'broken'.
OL,10,FShe said: "It is absolutely broken and
OL,11,Frenters have been let down. The rents
OL,12,Fhave increased by 64% over the last 10
OL,13,Fyears, which is twice as fast as
OL,14,Fpeople's income.
OL,16,F"In parallel, we've also got more than
OL,17,F20,000 people on the waiting list for
OL,18,Fa social home which is putting
OL,19,Fpressure on the private rental market.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
